Brazilian red meat production 1986 fell 20 pct 1.9 mln tonne due drought reduce slaughter weight herd rebuild start cattle price U.S. Agriculture Department said. In report World Production Trade Developments USDA 1987 beef production expect reach 2.3 mln tonnes. Pork production 1986 rise 83 pct 1.1 mln tonne due sharp rise beef price expect remain level USDA said. Reuter 